---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How MyTripTip collects limited data, uses cookies, and works with Google AdSense and affiliate partners."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how MyTripTip collects, uses, and protects information
      when you visit <strong>mytriptip.com</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p>
      We do not require account creation and we do not knowingly collect sensitive personal
      information directly through this website. Like most websites, we may receive limited
      technical data such as browser type, device information, referral source, and general
      analytics information through hosting, analytics, advertising, and affiliate partners.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
    <p>
      MyTripTip may use cookies and similar technologies to improve site performance,
      understand usage patterns, remember preferences, and support advertising and affiliate tracking.
    </p>

    <h2>Google AdSense and Advertising Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to serve ads based on a user's
      prior visits to this website or other websites.
    </p>
    <p>
      Google&apos;s use of advertising cookies enables Google and its partners to serve ads
      based on your visit to this site and/or other sites on the Internet.
    </p>
    <p>
      Users may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.
      You can also learn more about opting out of some third-party vendors&apos; personalized
      advertising by visiting
      <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      Some pages on MyTripTip contain affiliate links. If you click an affiliate link and make
      a booking or purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. Affiliate partners
      may use cookies or tracking parameters to attribute referrals.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We may work with third-party services such as Google AdSense, analytics providers, and
      affiliate platforms including Booking.com, Viator, and Airalo. These providers may collect
      information according to their own privacy policies.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You can disable or clear cookies in your browser settings.</li>
      <li>You can opt out of personalized ads through Google Ads Settings.</li>
      <li>You can avoid clicking affiliate links if you do not want referral tracking applied.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>
      We take reasonable steps to keep this website secure, but no method of transmission or storage
      is completely secure. Use the site with that understanding.
    </p>

    <h2>Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      This website is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal
      information from children.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time as the site, legal requirements, or
      advertising setup changes. The latest version on this page will apply.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
      <a href="mailto:hello@mytriptip.com">hello@mytriptip.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
